results.title: Yellow LIVE LAUGH LOVE Wine Cork Keychain Butterfly #K108
results.description:
Show your love for happiness, laughter, and life in general with this beautiful, handcrafted keychain made with a natural wine cork from SIMI! Adorned with beautiful, vintage yellow glass and ceramic beads, then accented with silvertone nickel-free alloy accentuating spacers, and finished with three silver charms, one a butterfly," another one a swirl design, and one with "LIVE, LAUGH, LOVE." You cannot help but smile and feel good when you see this in person!

This keychain measures approx 7" long.

*** Every keychain is one-of-a-kind and lovingly made just for you with quality materials that won’t fade nor tarnish. Beads are made from either natural stone, Czech crystals, vintage or new glass pieces, lampwork glass, and nickel-free metals for a vibrant and charming finish.

All of my cork keychains are made with natural red or white wine corks (and sometimes champagne, it will be noted in the description), and wired with a heavy-gauge #18 wire for strength and to retain its shape through many handling.

These beautiful keychains can also be enjoyed as suncatchers in a sunny window, car rear-view mirror hanging, or wherever you would like to enjoy its shimmering beauty!

No two keychains are ever alike, every single one features different designs and color variations, which is intentional! They are unique, just like you!

Thank you for looking! You can see more of our beautiful keychains, and, coming soon, earrings, suncatchers, zipper pulls, purse charms, and bracelet helping hands in our Vendi-Dem Creations store!
